column2: "That's all of the data that I have confirmed. Currently, there's no distinctive differences from our calculations."
"I agree, however, whether it's photons or ether, both of them are strongly influenced by emotions."
"Despite continuing your interactions, remain cautious. Please keep in mind to gather accurate information."
"Affirmative, Vice Commander."
"1. What are you two talking about?"
"2. What an unusual pairing. "
"You can see the Vice Commander?!"
"<%me>, just who ARE you?"
"It's alright, Aika. <%me> already knows everything about us."
"Really...? Even so, to be able to see you, Vice Commander... How is that even possible?"
"How nostalgic... I feel like I'm having the same reaction from our first meeting, <%me>."
"Vice Commander... I wish that you had informed us about this information beforehand."
"Even I have my own secrets."
"Isn't it the same with you, Aika? Like your time down on Earth."
"If you're referring to Itsuki and Rina, then it's not something that's worth keeping secret."
"However, during your stay, images of you in a waitress outfit had begun to spread around."
"W-Where did you get that from?!"
"Somehow it just came to me. From Casra."
"Tch! I have urgent business that I need to deal with immediately! Please, excuse me!"
"I apologise for the trouble, <%me>."
"Aika's feelings towards Earth are strong and I thought that she's pushing herself too much. I guess that was a good breather for her. "
"Additionally, if that mischievous four-eyes gets blamed along the way, that's two birds with one stone."
